de.linearbits.jhpl

Class LatticeHighdimensional<T,U>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.linearbits.jhpl.Lattice<T,U>
      • de.linearbits.jhpl.LatticeHighdimensional<T,U>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of values in the dimensions of the lattice
    U - The type of associated data

    public class LatticeHighdimensional<T,U>
extends Lattice<T,U>
    This class implements an extension of the basic lattice without any restrictions on the number of nodes.
